overview: Invicta FC 20: Evinger vs. Kunitsakaya was a mixed martial arts event that was headlined by Invicta FC bantamweight champion Tonya Evinger defending her title against Russian newcomer Yana Kunitsakaya. In the co-main event, strawweight champion Angela Hill defended against Kaline Medeiros.
title: Invicta FC 20: Evinger vs. Kunitskaya
